30using VariableSet = std::unordered_set<const TVariable *>;
31using VariableList = std::vector<const TVariable *>;

33////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////

35struct PipelineStructInfo
36{
37 VariableSet pipelineVariables;
38 PipelineScoped<TStructure> pipelineStruct;
39 const TFunction *funcOriginalToModified = nullptr;
40 const TFunction *funcModifiedToOriginal = nullptr;
41
42 bool isEmpty() const
43 {
44 if (pipelineStruct.isTotallyEmpty())
45 {
46 ASSERT(pipelineVariables.empty());
47 return true;
48 }
49 else
50 {
51 ASSERT(pipelineStruct.isTotallyFull());
52 ASSERT(!pipelineVariables.empty());
53 return false;
54 }
55 }
56};
57
58class GeneratePipelineStruct : private TIntermRebuild
59{
60 private:
61 const Pipeline &mPipeline;
62 SymbolEnv &mSymbolEnv;
63 Invariants &mInvariants;
64 VariableList mPipelineVariableList;
65 IdGen &mIdGen;
66 PipelineStructInfo mInfo;
67
68 public:
69 static bool Exec(PipelineStructInfo &out,
70 TCompiler &compiler,
71 TIntermBlock &root,
72 IdGen &idGen,
73 const Pipeline &pipeline,
74 SymbolEnv &symbolEnv,
75 Invariants &invariants)
76 {
77 GeneratePipelineStruct self(compiler, idGen, pipeline, symbolEnv, invariants);
78 if (!self.exec(root))
79 {
80 return false;
81 }
82 out = self.mInfo;
83 return true;
84 }
85
86 private:
87 GeneratePipelineStruct(TCompiler &compiler,
88 IdGen &idGen,
89 const Pipeline &pipeline,
90 SymbolEnv &symbolEnv,
91 Invariants &invariants)
92 : TIntermRebuild(compiler, true, true),
93 mPipeline(pipeline),
94 mSymbolEnv(symbolEnv),
95 mInvariants(invariants),
96 mIdGen(idGen)
97 {}
98
99 bool exec(TIntermBlock &root)
100 {
101 if (!rebuildRoot(root))
102 {
103 return false;
104 }
105
106 if (mInfo.pipelineVariables.empty())
107 {
108 return true;
109 }
110
111 TIntermSequence seq;
112
113 const TStructure &pipelineStruct = [&]() -> const TStructure & {
114 if (mPipeline.globalInstanceVar)
115 {
116 return *mPipeline.globalInstanceVar->getType().getStruct();
117 }
118 else
119 {
120 return createInternalPipelineStruct(root, seq);
121 }
122 }();
123
124 ModifiedStructMachineries modifiedMachineries;
125 const bool isUBO = mPipeline.type == Pipeline::Type::UniformBuffer;
126 const bool modified = TryCreateModifiedStruct(mCompiler,
127 mSymbolEnv, mIdGen, mPipeline.externalStructModifyConfig(), pipelineStruct,
128 mPipeline.getStructTypeName(Pipeline::Variant::Modified),
129 modifiedMachineries, isUBO, !isUBO);
130
131 if (modified)
132 {
133 ASSERT(mPipeline.type != Pipeline::Type::Texture);
134 ASSERT(mPipeline.type == Pipeline::Type::AngleUniforms || !mPipeline.globalInstanceVar); // This shouldn't happen by construction.
135
136 auto getFunction = [](sh::TIntermFunctionDefinition *funcDecl) {
137 return funcDecl ? funcDecl->getFunction() : nullptr;
138 };
139
140 const size_t size = modifiedMachineries.size();
141 ASSERT(size > 0);
142 for (size_t i = 0; i < size; ++i)
143 {
144 const ModifiedStructMachinery &machinery = modifiedMachineries.at(i);
145 ASSERT(machinery.modifiedStruct);
146
147 seq.push_back(new TIntermDeclaration{
148 &CreateStructTypeVariable(mSymbolTable, *machinery.modifiedStruct)});
149
150 if (mPipeline.isPipelineOut())
151 {
152 ASSERT(machinery.funcOriginalToModified);
153 ASSERT(!machinery.funcModifiedToOriginal);
154 seq.push_back(machinery.funcOriginalToModified);
155 }
156 else
157 {
158 ASSERT(machinery.funcModifiedToOriginal);
159 ASSERT(!machinery.funcOriginalToModified);
160 seq.push_back(machinery.funcModifiedToOriginal);
161 }
162
163 if (i == size - 1)
164 {
165 mInfo.funcOriginalToModified = getFunction(machinery.funcOriginalToModified);
166 mInfo.funcModifiedToOriginal = getFunction(machinery.funcModifiedToOriginal);
167
168 mInfo.pipelineStruct.internal = &pipelineStruct;
169 mInfo.pipelineStruct.external =
170 modified ? machinery.modifiedStruct : &pipelineStruct;
171 }
172 }
173 }
174 else
175 {
176 mInfo.pipelineStruct.internal = &pipelineStruct;
177 mInfo.pipelineStruct.external = &pipelineStruct;
178 }
179
180 root.insertChildNodes(FindMainIndex(&root), seq);
181
182 return true;
183 }
184
185 private:
186 PreResult visitFunctionDefinitionPre(TIntermFunctionDefinition &node) override
187 {
188 return {node, VisitBits::Neither};
189 }
190 PostResult visitDeclarationPost(TIntermDeclaration &declNode) override
191 {
192 Declaration decl = ViewDeclaration(declNode);
193 const TVariable &var = decl.symbol.variable();
194 if (mPipeline.uses(var))
195 {
196 ASSERT(mInfo.pipelineVariables.find(&var) == mInfo.pipelineVariables.end());
197 mInfo.pipelineVariables.insert(&var);
198 mPipelineVariableList.push_back(&var);
199 return nullptr;
200 }
201
202 return declNode;
203 }
204
205 const TStructure &createInternalPipelineStruct(TIntermBlock &root, TIntermSequence &outDeclSeq)
206 {
207 auto &fields = *new TFieldList();
208
209 switch (mPipeline.type)
210 {
211 case Pipeline::Type::Texture:
212 {
213 for (const TVariable *var : mPipelineVariableList)
214 {
215 ASSERT(!mInvariants.contains(*var));
216 const TType &varType = var->getType();
217 const TBasicType samplerType = varType.getBasicType();
218
219 const TStructure &textureEnv = mSymbolEnv.getTextureEnv(samplerType);
220 auto *textureEnvType = new TType(&textureEnv, false);
221 if (varType.isArray())
222 {
223 textureEnvType->makeArrays(varType.getArraySizes());
224 }
225
226 fields.push_back(
227 new TField(textureEnvType, var->name(), kNoSourceLoc, var->symbolType()));
228 }
229 }
230 break;
231
232 case Pipeline::Type::UniformBuffer:
233 {
234 for (const TVariable *var : mPipelineVariableList)
235 {
236 auto &type = CloneType(var->getType());
237 auto *field = new TField(&type, var->name(), kNoSourceLoc, var->symbolType());
238 mSymbolEnv.markAsPointer(*field, AddressSpace::Constant);
239 mSymbolEnv.markAsUBO(*field);
240 mSymbolEnv.markAsPointer(*var, AddressSpace::Constant);
241 fields.push_back(field);
242 }
243 }
244 break;
245 default:
246 {
247 for (const TVariable *var : mPipelineVariableList)
248 {
249 auto &type = CloneType(var->getType());
250 auto *field = new TField(&type, var->name(), kNoSourceLoc, var->symbolType());
251 fields.push_back(field);
252
253 if (mInvariants.contains(*var))
254 {
255 mInvariants.insert(*field);
256 }
257 }
258 }
259 break;
260 }
261
262 Name pipelineStructName = mPipeline.getStructTypeName(Pipeline::Variant::Original);
263 auto &s = *new TStructure(&mSymbolTable, pipelineStructName.rawName(), &fields,
264 pipelineStructName.symbolType());
265
266 outDeclSeq.push_back(new TIntermDeclaration{&CreateStructTypeVariable(mSymbolTable, s)});
267
268 return s;
269 }
270};
271
272////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
273
274PipelineScoped<TVariable> CreatePipelineMainLocalVar(TSymbolTable &symbolTable,
275 const Pipeline &pipeline,
276 PipelineScoped<TStructure> pipelineStruct)
277{
278 ASSERT(pipelineStruct.isTotallyFull());
279
280 PipelineScoped<TVariable> pipelineMainLocalVar;
281
282 auto populateExternalMainLocalVar = [&]() {
283 ASSERT(!pipelineMainLocalVar.external);
284 pipelineMainLocalVar.external = &CreateInstanceVariable(
285 symbolTable, *pipelineStruct.external,
286 pipeline.getStructInstanceName(pipelineStruct.isUniform()
287 ? Pipeline::Variant::Original
288 : Pipeline::Variant::Modified));
289 };
290
291 auto populateDistinctInternalMainLocalVar = [&]() {
292 ASSERT(!pipelineMainLocalVar.internal);
293 pipelineMainLocalVar.internal =
294 &CreateInstanceVariable(symbolTable, *pipelineStruct.internal,
295 pipeline.getStructInstanceName(Pipeline::Variant::Original));
296 };
297
298 if (pipeline.type == Pipeline::Type::InstanceId)
299 {
300 populateDistinctInternalMainLocalVar();
301 }
302 else if (pipeline.alwaysRequiresLocalVariableDeclarationInMain())
303 {
304 populateExternalMainLocalVar();
305
306 if (pipelineStruct.isUniform())
307 {
308 pipelineMainLocalVar.internal = pipelineMainLocalVar.external;
309 }
310 else
311 {
312 populateDistinctInternalMainLocalVar();
313 }
314 }
315 else if (!pipelineStruct.isUniform())
316 {
317 populateDistinctInternalMainLocalVar();
318 }
319
320 return pipelineMainLocalVar;
321}
322
323class PipelineFunctionEnv
324{
325 private:
326 TCompiler &mCompiler;
327 SymbolEnv &mSymbolEnv;
328 TSymbolTable &mSymbolTable;
329 IdGen &mIdGen;
330 const Pipeline &mPipeline;
331 const std::unordered_set<const TFunction *> &mPipelineFunctions;
332 const PipelineScoped<TStructure> mPipelineStruct;
333 PipelineScoped<TVariable> &mPipelineMainLocalVar;
334
335 std::unordered_map<const TFunction *, const TFunction *> mFuncMap;
336
337 public:
338 PipelineFunctionEnv(TCompiler &compiler,
339 SymbolEnv &symbolEnv,
340 IdGen &idGen,
341 const Pipeline &pipeline,
342 const std::unordered_set<const TFunction *> &pipelineFunctions,
343 PipelineScoped<TStructure> pipelineStruct,
344 PipelineScoped<TVariable> &pipelineMainLocalVar)
345 : mCompiler(compiler),
346 mSymbolEnv(symbolEnv),
347 mSymbolTable(symbolEnv.symbolTable()),
348 mIdGen(idGen),
349 mPipeline(pipeline),
350 mPipelineFunctions(pipelineFunctions),
351 mPipelineStruct(pipelineStruct),
352 mPipelineMainLocalVar(pipelineMainLocalVar)
353 {}
354
355 bool isOriginalPipelineFunction(const TFunction &func) const
356 {
357 return mPipelineFunctions.find(&func) != mPipelineFunctions.end();
358 }
359
360 bool isUpdatedPipelineFunction(const TFunction &func) const
361 {
362 auto it = mFuncMap.find(&func);
363 if (it == mFuncMap.end())
364 {
365 return false;
366 }
367 return &func == it->second;
368 }
369
370 const TFunction &getUpdatedFunction(const TFunction &func)
371 {
372 ASSERT(isOriginalPipelineFunction(func) || isUpdatedPipelineFunction(func));
373
374 const TFunction *newFunc;
375
376 auto it = mFuncMap.find(&func);
377 if (it == mFuncMap.end())
378 {
379 const bool isMain = func.isMain();
380
381 if (isMain && mPipeline.isPipelineOut())
382 {
383 ASSERT(func.getReturnType().getBasicType() == TBasicType::EbtVoid);
384 newFunc = &CloneFunctionAndChangeReturnType(mSymbolTable, nullptr, func,
385 *mPipelineStruct.external);
386 }
387 else if (isMain && (mPipeline.type == Pipeline::Type::InvocationVertexGlobals ||
388 mPipeline.type == Pipeline::Type::InvocationFragmentGlobals))
389 {
390 std::vector<const TVariable *> variables;
391 for (const TField *field : mPipelineStruct.external->fields())
392 {
393 variables.push_back(new TVariable(&mSymbolTable, field->name(), field->type(),
394 field->symbolType()));
395 }
396 newFunc = &CloneFunctionAndAppendParams(mSymbolTable, nullptr, func, variables);
397 }
398 else if (isMain && mPipeline.type == Pipeline::Type::Texture)
399 {
400 std::vector<const TVariable *> variables;
401 TranslatorMetalReflection *reflection =
402 ((sh::TranslatorMetalDirect *)&mCompiler)->getTranslatorMetalReflection();
403 for (const TField *field : mPipelineStruct.external->fields())
404 {
405 const TStructure *textureEnv = field->type()->getStruct();
406 ASSERT(textureEnv && textureEnv->fields().size() == 2);
407 for (const TField *subfield : textureEnv->fields())
408 {
409 const Name name = mIdGen.createNewName({field->name(), subfield->name()});
410 TType &type = *new TType(*subfield->type());
411 ASSERT(!type.isArray());
412 type.makeArrays(field->type()->getArraySizes());
413 auto *var =
414 new TVariable(&mSymbolTable, name.rawName(), &type, name.symbolType());
415 variables.push_back(var);
416 reflection->addOriginalName(var->uniqueId().get(), field->name().data());
417 }
418 }
419 newFunc = &CloneFunctionAndAppendParams(mSymbolTable, nullptr, func, variables);
420 }
421 else if (isMain && mPipeline.type == Pipeline::Type::InstanceId)
422 {
423 Name name = mPipeline.getStructInstanceName(Pipeline::Variant::Modified);
424 auto *var = new TVariable(&mSymbolTable, name.rawName(),
425 new TType(TBasicType::EbtUInt), name.symbolType());
426 newFunc = &CloneFunctionAndPrependParam(mSymbolTable, nullptr, func, *var);
427 mPipelineMainLocalVar.external = var;
428 }
429 else if (isMain && mPipeline.alwaysRequiresLocalVariableDeclarationInMain())
430 {
431 ASSERT(mPipelineMainLocalVar.isTotallyFull());
432 newFunc = &func;
433 }
434 else
435 {
436 const TVariable *var;
437 AddressSpace addressSpace;
438
439 if (isMain && !mPipelineMainLocalVar.isUniform())
440 {
441 var = &CreateInstanceVariable(
442 mSymbolTable, *mPipelineStruct.external,
443 mPipeline.getStructInstanceName(Pipeline::Variant::Modified));
444 addressSpace = mPipeline.externalAddressSpace();
445 }
446 else
447 {
448 if (mPipeline.type == Pipeline::Type::UniformBuffer)
449 {
450 TranslatorMetalReflection *reflection =
451 ((sh::TranslatorMetalDirect *)&mCompiler)->getTranslatorMetalReflection();
452 // TODO: need more checks to make sure they line up? Could be reordered?
453 ASSERT(mPipelineStruct.external->fields().size() ==
454 mPipelineStruct.internal->fields().size());
455 for (size_t i = 0; i < mPipelineStruct.external->fields().size(); i++)
456 {
457 const TField *externalField = mPipelineStruct.external->fields()[i];
458 const TField *internalField = mPipelineStruct.internal->fields()[i];
459 const TType &externalType = *externalField->type();
460 const TType &internalType = *internalField->type();
461 ASSERT(externalType.getBasicType() == internalType.getBasicType());
462 if (externalType.getBasicType() == TBasicType::EbtStruct)
463 {
464 const TStructure *externalEnv = externalType.getStruct();
465 const TStructure *internalEnv = internalType.getStruct();
466 const std::string internalName = reflection->getOriginalName(internalEnv->uniqueId().get());
467 reflection->addOriginalName(externalEnv->uniqueId().get(), internalName);
468 }
469 }
470 }
471 var = &CreateInstanceVariable(
472 mSymbolTable, *mPipelineStruct.internal,
473 mPipeline.getStructInstanceName(Pipeline::Variant::Original));
474 addressSpace = mPipelineMainLocalVar.isUniform()
475 ? mPipeline.externalAddressSpace()
476 : AddressSpace::Thread;
477 }
478
479 bool markAsReference = true;
480 if (isMain)
481 {
482 switch (mPipeline.type)
483 {
484 case Pipeline::Type::VertexIn:
485 case Pipeline::Type::FragmentIn:
486 markAsReference = false;
487 break;
488
489 default:
490 break;
491 }
492 }
493
494 if (markAsReference)
495 {
496 mSymbolEnv.markAsReference(*var, addressSpace);
497 }
498
499 newFunc = &CloneFunctionAndPrependParam(mSymbolTable, nullptr, func, *var);
500 }
501
502 mFuncMap[&func] = newFunc;
503 mFuncMap[newFunc] = newFunc;
504 }
505 else
506 {
507 newFunc = it->second;
508 }
509
510 return *newFunc;
511 }
512
513 TIntermFunctionPrototype *createUpdatedFunctionPrototype(
514 TIntermFunctionPrototype &funcProtoNode)
515 {
516 const TFunction &func = *funcProtoNode.getFunction();
517 if (!isOriginalPipelineFunction(func) && !isUpdatedPipelineFunction(func))
518 {
519 return nullptr;
520 }
521 const TFunction &newFunc = getUpdatedFunction(func);
522 return new TIntermFunctionPrototype(&newFunc);
523 }
524};
525
526class UpdatePipelineFunctions : private TIntermRebuild
527{
528 private:
529 const Pipeline &mPipeline;
530 const PipelineScoped<TStructure> mPipelineStruct;
531 PipelineScoped<TVariable> &mPipelineMainLocalVar;
532 SymbolEnv &mSymbolEnv;
533 PipelineFunctionEnv mEnv;
534 const TFunction *mFuncOriginalToModified;
535 const TFunction *mFuncModifiedToOriginal;
536
537 public:
538 static bool ThreadPipeline(TCompiler &compiler,
539 TIntermBlock &root,
540 const Pipeline &pipeline,
541 const std::unordered_set<const TFunction *> &pipelineFunctions,
542 PipelineScoped<TStructure> pipelineStruct,
543 PipelineScoped<TVariable> &pipelineMainLocalVar,
544 IdGen &idGen,
545 SymbolEnv &symbolEnv,
546 const TFunction *funcOriginalToModified,
547 const TFunction *funcModifiedToOriginal)
548 {
549 UpdatePipelineFunctions self(compiler, pipeline, pipelineFunctions, pipelineStruct,
550 pipelineMainLocalVar, idGen, symbolEnv, funcOriginalToModified,
551 funcModifiedToOriginal);
552 if (!self.rebuildRoot(root))
553 {
554 return false;
555 }
556 return true;
557 }
558
559 private:
560 UpdatePipelineFunctions(TCompiler &compiler,
561 const Pipeline &pipeline,
562 const std::unordered_set<const TFunction *> &pipelineFunctions,
563 PipelineScoped<TStructure> pipelineStruct,
564 PipelineScoped<TVariable> &pipelineMainLocalVar,
565 IdGen &idGen,
566 SymbolEnv &symbolEnv,
567 const TFunction *funcOriginalToModified,
568 const TFunction *funcModifiedToOriginal)
569 : TIntermRebuild(compiler, false, true),
570 mPipeline(pipeline),
571 mPipelineStruct(pipelineStruct),
572 mPipelineMainLocalVar(pipelineMainLocalVar),
573 mSymbolEnv(symbolEnv),
574 mEnv(compiler,
575 symbolEnv,
576 idGen,
577 pipeline,
578 pipelineFunctions,
579 pipelineStruct,
580 mPipelineMainLocalVar),
581 mFuncOriginalToModified(funcOriginalToModified),
582 mFuncModifiedToOriginal(funcModifiedToOriginal)
583 {
584 ASSERT(mPipelineStruct.isTotallyFull());
585 }
586
587 const TVariable &getInternalPipelineVariable(const TFunction &pipelineFunc)
588 {
589 if (pipelineFunc.isMain() && (mPipeline.alwaysRequiresLocalVariableDeclarationInMain() ||
590 !mPipelineMainLocalVar.isUniform()))
591 {
592 ASSERT(mPipelineMainLocalVar.internal);
593 return *mPipelineMainLocalVar.internal;
594 }
595 else
596 {
597 ASSERT(pipelineFunc.getParamCount() > 0);
598 return *pipelineFunc.getParam(0);
599 }
600 }
601
602 const TVariable &getExternalPipelineVariable(const TFunction &mainFunc)
603 {
604 ASSERT(mainFunc.isMain());
605 if (mPipelineMainLocalVar.external)
606 {
607 return *mPipelineMainLocalVar.external;
608 }
609 else
610 {
611 ASSERT(mainFunc.getParamCount() > 0);
612 return *mainFunc.getParam(0);
613 }
614 }
615
616 PostResult visitAggregatePost(TIntermAggregate &callNode) override
617 {
618 if (callNode.isConstructor())
619 {
620 return callNode;
621 }
622 else
623 {
624 const TFunction &oldCalledFunc = *callNode.getFunction();
625 if (!mEnv.isOriginalPipelineFunction(oldCalledFunc))
626 {
627 return callNode;
628 }
629 const TFunction &newCalledFunc = mEnv.getUpdatedFunction(oldCalledFunc);
630
631 const TFunction *oldOwnerFunc = getParentFunction();
632 ASSERT(oldOwnerFunc);
633 const TFunction &newOwnerFunc = mEnv.getUpdatedFunction(*oldOwnerFunc);
634
635 return *TIntermAggregate::CreateFunctionCall(
636 newCalledFunc, &CloneSequenceAndPrepend(
637 *callNode.getSequence(),
638 *new TIntermSymbol(&getInternalPipelineVariable(newOwnerFunc))));
639 }
640 }
641
642 PostResult visitFunctionPrototypePost(TIntermFunctionPrototype &funcProtoNode) override
643 {
644 TIntermFunctionPrototype *newFuncProtoNode =
645 mEnv.createUpdatedFunctionPrototype(funcProtoNode);
646 if (newFuncProtoNode == nullptr)
647 {
648 return funcProtoNode;
649 }
650 return *newFuncProtoNode;
651 }
652
653 PostResult visitFunctionDefinitionPost(TIntermFunctionDefinition &funcDefNode) override
654 {
655 if (funcDefNode.getFunction()->isMain())
656 {
657 return visitMain(funcDefNode);
658 }
659 else
660 {
661 return visitNonMain(funcDefNode);
662 }
663 }
664
665 TIntermNode &visitNonMain(TIntermFunctionDefinition &funcDefNode)
666 {
667 TIntermFunctionPrototype &funcProtoNode = *funcDefNode.getFunctionPrototype();
668 ASSERT(!funcProtoNode.getFunction()->isMain());
669
670 TIntermFunctionPrototype *newFuncProtoNode =
671 mEnv.createUpdatedFunctionPrototype(funcProtoNode);
672 if (newFuncProtoNode == nullptr)
673 {
674 return funcDefNode;
675 }
676
677 const TFunction &func = *newFuncProtoNode->getFunction();
678 ASSERT(!func.isMain());
679
680 TIntermBlock *body = funcDefNode.getBody();
681
682 return *new TIntermFunctionDefinition(newFuncProtoNode, body);
683 }
684
685 TIntermNode &visitMain(TIntermFunctionDefinition &funcDefNode)
686 {
687 TIntermFunctionPrototype &funcProtoNode = *funcDefNode.getFunctionPrototype();
688 ASSERT(funcProtoNode.getFunction()->isMain());
689
690 TIntermFunctionPrototype *newFuncProtoNode =
691 mEnv.createUpdatedFunctionPrototype(funcProtoNode);
692 if (newFuncProtoNode == nullptr)
693 {
694 return funcDefNode;
695 }
696
697 const TFunction &func = *newFuncProtoNode->getFunction();
698 ASSERT(func.isMain());
699
700 auto callModifiedToOriginal = [&](TIntermBlock &body) {
701 ASSERT(mPipelineMainLocalVar.internal);
702 if (!mPipeline.isPipelineOut())
703 {
704 ASSERT(mFuncModifiedToOriginal);
705 auto *m = new TIntermSymbol(&getExternalPipelineVariable(func));
706 auto *o = new TIntermSymbol(mPipelineMainLocalVar.internal);
707 body.appendStatement(TIntermAggregate::CreateFunctionCall(
708 *mFuncModifiedToOriginal, new TIntermSequence{m, o}));
709 }
710 };
711
712 auto callOriginalToModified = [&](TIntermBlock &body) {
713 ASSERT(mPipelineMainLocalVar.internal);
714 if (mPipeline.isPipelineOut())
715 {
716 ASSERT(mFuncOriginalToModified);
717 auto *o = new TIntermSymbol(mPipelineMainLocalVar.internal);
718 auto *m = new TIntermSymbol(&getExternalPipelineVariable(func));
719 body.appendStatement(TIntermAggregate::CreateFunctionCall(
720 *mFuncOriginalToModified, new TIntermSequence{o, m}));
721 }
722 };
723
724 TIntermBlock *body = funcDefNode.getBody();
725
726 if (mPipeline.alwaysRequiresLocalVariableDeclarationInMain())
727 {
728 ASSERT(mPipelineMainLocalVar.isTotallyFull());
729
730 auto *newBody = new TIntermBlock();
731 newBody->appendStatement(new TIntermDeclaration{mPipelineMainLocalVar.internal});
732
733 if (mPipeline.type == Pipeline::Type::InvocationVertexGlobals ||
734 mPipeline.type == Pipeline::Type::InvocationFragmentGlobals)
735 {
736 // Populate struct instance with references to global pipeline variables.
737 for (const TField *field : mPipelineStruct.external->fields())
738 {
739 auto *var = new TVariable(&mSymbolTable, field->name(), field->type(),
740 field->symbolType());
741 auto *symbol = new TIntermSymbol(var);
742 auto &accessNode = AccessField(*mPipelineMainLocalVar.internal, var->name());
743 auto *assignNode = new TIntermBinary(TOperator::EOpAssign, &accessNode, symbol);
744 newBody->appendStatement(assignNode);
745 }
746 }
747 else if (mPipeline.type == Pipeline::Type::Texture)
748 {
749 const TFieldList &fields = mPipelineStruct.external->fields();
750
751 ASSERT(func.getParamCount() >= 2 * fields.size());
752 size_t paramIndex = func.getParamCount() - 2 * fields.size();
753
754 for (const TField *field : fields)
755 {
756 const TVariable &textureParam = *func.getParam(paramIndex++);
757 const TVariable &samplerParam = *func.getParam(paramIndex++);
758
759 auto go = [&](TIntermTyped &env, const int *index) {
760 TIntermTyped &textureField = AccessField(
761 AccessIndex(*env.deepCopy(), index), ImmutableString("texture"));
762 TIntermTyped &samplerField = AccessField(
763 AccessIndex(*env.deepCopy(), index), ImmutableString("sampler"));
764
765 auto mkAssign = [&](TIntermTyped &field, const TVariable &param) {
766 return new TIntermBinary(TOperator::EOpAssign, &field,
767 &mSymbolEnv.callFunctionOverload(
768 Name("addressof"), field.getType(),
769 *new TIntermSequence{&AccessIndex(
770 *new TIntermSymbol(&param), index)}));
771 };
772
773 newBody->appendStatement(mkAssign(textureField, textureParam));
774 newBody->appendStatement(mkAssign(samplerField, samplerParam));
775 };
776
777 TIntermTyped &env = AccessField(*mPipelineMainLocalVar.internal, field->name());
778 const TType &envType = env.getType();
779
780 if (envType.isArray())
781 {
782 ASSERT(!envType.isArrayOfArrays());
783 const auto n = static_cast<int>(envType.getArraySizeProduct());
784 for (int i = 0; i < n; ++i)
785 {
786 go(env, &i);
787 }
788 }
789 else
790 {
791 go(env, nullptr);
792 }
793 }
794 }
795 else if (mPipeline.type == Pipeline::Type::InstanceId)
796 {
797 newBody->appendStatement(new TIntermBinary(
798 TOperator::EOpAssign,
799 &AccessFieldByIndex(*new TIntermSymbol(&getInternalPipelineVariable(func)), 0),
800 &AsType(mSymbolEnv, *new TType(TBasicType::EbtInt),
801 *new TIntermSymbol(&getExternalPipelineVariable(func)))));
802 }
803 else if (!mPipelineMainLocalVar.isUniform())
804 {
805 newBody->appendStatement(new TIntermDeclaration{mPipelineMainLocalVar.external});
806 callModifiedToOriginal(*newBody);
807 }
808
809 newBody->appendStatement(body);
810
811 if (!mPipelineMainLocalVar.isUniform())
812 {
813 callOriginalToModified(*newBody);
814 }
815
816 if (mPipeline.isPipelineOut())
817 {
818 newBody->appendStatement(new TIntermBranch(
819 TOperator::EOpReturn, new TIntermSymbol(mPipelineMainLocalVar.external)));
820 }
821
822 body = newBody;
823 }
824 else if (!mPipelineMainLocalVar.isUniform())
825 {
826 ASSERT(!mPipelineMainLocalVar.external);
827 ASSERT(mPipelineMainLocalVar.internal);
828
829 auto *newBody = new TIntermBlock();
830 newBody->appendStatement(new TIntermDeclaration{mPipelineMainLocalVar.internal});
831 callModifiedToOriginal(*newBody);
832 newBody->appendStatement(body);
833 callOriginalToModified(*newBody);
834 body = newBody;
835 }
836
837 return *new TIntermFunctionDefinition(newFuncProtoNode, body);
838 }
839};
840
841////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
842
843bool UpdatePipelineSymbols(Pipeline::Type pipelineType,
844 TCompiler &compiler,
845 TIntermBlock &root,
846 SymbolEnv &symbolEnv,
847 const VariableSet &pipelineVariables,
848 PipelineScoped<TVariable> pipelineMainLocalVar)
849{
850 auto map = [&](const TFunction *owner, TIntermSymbol &symbol) -> TIntermNode & {
851 const TVariable &var = symbol.variable();
852 if (pipelineVariables.find(&var) == pipelineVariables.end())
853 {
854 return symbol;
855 }
856 ASSERT(owner);
857 const TVariable *structInstanceVar;
858 if (owner->isMain())
859 {
860 ASSERT(pipelineMainLocalVar.internal);
861 structInstanceVar = pipelineMainLocalVar.internal;
862 }
863 else
864 {
865 ASSERT(owner->getParamCount() > 0);
866 structInstanceVar = owner->getParam(0);
867 }
868 ASSERT(structInstanceVar);
869 return AccessField(*structInstanceVar, var.name());
870 };
871 return MapSymbols(compiler, root, map);
872}
873
874////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
875
876bool RewritePipeline(TCompiler &compiler,
877 TIntermBlock &root,
878 IdGen &idGen,
879 const Pipeline &pipeline,
880 SymbolEnv &symbolEnv,
881 Invariants &invariants,
882 PipelineScoped<TStructure> &outStruct)
883{
884 ASSERT(outStruct.isTotallyEmpty());
885
886 TSymbolTable &symbolTable = compiler.getSymbolTable();
887
888 PipelineStructInfo psi;
889 if (!GeneratePipelineStruct::Exec(psi, compiler, root, idGen, pipeline, symbolEnv, invariants))
890 {
891 return false;
892 }
893
894 if (psi.isEmpty())
895 {
896 return true;
897 }
898
899 const auto pipelineFunctions = DiscoverDependentFunctions(root, [&](const TVariable &var) {
900 return psi.pipelineVariables.find(&var) != psi.pipelineVariables.end();
901 });
902
903 auto pipelineMainLocalVar =
904 CreatePipelineMainLocalVar(symbolTable, pipeline, psi.pipelineStruct);
905
906 if (!UpdatePipelineFunctions::ThreadPipeline(
907 compiler, root, pipeline, pipelineFunctions, psi.pipelineStruct, pipelineMainLocalVar,
908 idGen, symbolEnv, psi.funcOriginalToModified, psi.funcModifiedToOriginal))
909 {
910 return false;
911 }
912
913 if (!pipeline.globalInstanceVar)
914 {
915 if (!UpdatePipelineSymbols(pipeline.type, compiler, root, symbolEnv, psi.pipelineVariables,
916 pipelineMainLocalVar))
917 {
918 return false;
919 }
920 }
921
922 if (!PruneNoOps(&compiler, &root, &compiler.getSymbolTable()))
923 {
924 return false;
925 }
926
927 outStruct = psi.pipelineStruct;
928 return true;
929}
930
931} // anonymous namespace
932
933bool sh::RewritePipelines(TCompiler &compiler,
934 TIntermBlock &root,
935 IdGen &idGen,
936 const TVariable &angleUniformsGlobalInstanceVar,
937 SymbolEnv &symbolEnv,
938 Invariants &invariants,
939 PipelineStructs &outStructs)
940{
941 struct Info
942 {
943 Pipeline::Type pipelineType;
944 PipelineScoped<TStructure> &outStruct;
945 const TVariable *globalInstanceVar;
946 };
947
948 Info infos[] = {
949 {Pipeline::Type::InstanceId, outStructs.instanceId, nullptr},
950 {Pipeline::Type::Texture, outStructs.texture, nullptr},
951 {Pipeline::Type::NonConstantGlobals, outStructs.nonConstantGlobals, nullptr},
952 {Pipeline::Type::AngleUniforms, outStructs.angleUniforms, &angleUniformsGlobalInstanceVar},
953 {Pipeline::Type::UserUniforms, outStructs.userUniforms, nullptr},
954 {Pipeline::Type::VertexIn, outStructs.vertexIn, nullptr},
955 {Pipeline::Type::VertexOut, outStructs.vertexOut, nullptr},
956 {Pipeline::Type::FragmentIn, outStructs.fragmentIn, nullptr},
957 {Pipeline::Type::FragmentOut, outStructs.fragmentOut, nullptr},
958 {Pipeline::Type::InvocationVertexGlobals, outStructs.invocationVertexGlobals, nullptr},
959 {Pipeline::Type::InvocationFragmentGlobals, outStructs.invocationFragmentGlobals, nullptr},
960 {Pipeline::Type::UniformBuffer, outStructs.uniformBuffers, nullptr},
961 };
962
963 for (Info &info : infos)
964 {
965 Pipeline pipeline{info.pipelineType, info.globalInstanceVar};
966 if (!RewritePipeline(compiler, root, idGen, pipeline, symbolEnv, invariants,
967 info.outStruct))
968 {
969 return false;
970 }
971 }
972
973 return true;
974}
